item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

[quote=“ox random xi, post:11, topic:508850”][quote author=sk8rdude461 link=topic=627092.msg4262735#msg4262735 date=1363617801]

lost my pass on nrs3 server anyway to recover it , i hosted the source a long while ago , and then i stopped now im back to train on it wont be hosting only using it on localhost but idk what my password is i need help!!

Edit the .p file? The password may be visible.

its not visible at all , i mean i’ve tried everything.

and you cannot transfer your data files because its encrypted i think it shows weird signs.

It’s not encrypted. The file editor you were using doesn’t support a .p file.
[/quote]
It might just be .bin too.[/quote]
718’s save character data in .p files. It’s nothing to do with the bin. I remember when I first (only time too) messed with 700+ I edited a .p, and some contents were readable with notepad++. Not all though.
